name: Recreation & Fitness Center (The Fit)
directions: The restroom, room 169, is located in the pool area on the eastern side of the building. Enter either through the main entrance or patio entrance (you will have to swipe your student card or pay to get in), turn right down the hallway towards the pool, enter the double doors to the pool area, turn left and room 169 "Family Changing Room" will be directly ahead.
comment: This family changing room includes not only a toilet and sink, but also an ADA-compliant shower, a bench, and lockers.

name: Murphy Hall
directions:
To get to the accessible restroom in room 217, enter the building, proceed through the door on the far left of the lobby, and the accessible restroom room 217 will be the third door on your right down the hallway.  
**There is also another NON-accessible restroom in room 223 in the lobby, immediately on the right after entering the building.
comment: Both restrooms (217 and 223) are labeled as "RESTROOM" with raised lettering and braille.  Also, room 217 is very spacious.
